snippet.title: TRAILER: Tryhard - upcoming indie sports RPG about managing a rugby club in New Zealand
snippet.description:
Tryhard is an upcoming sports RPG about managing an underdog rugby club in New Zealand. https://tryhardgame.com

WISHLIST ON STEAM: https://store.steampowered.com/app/3443270/Tryhard/
